Package: fcwtr
Type: Package
Title: Fast Continuous Wavelet Transform
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Lukas", "Schneiderbauer",
        email = "lukas.schneiderbauer@gmail.com",
        role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Lukas P. A.", "Arts", role = "cph"),
    person("Egon L.", "van den Broek", role = "cph"))
Maintainer: Lukas Schneiderbauer <lukas.schneiderbauer@gmail.com>
Description: Bundles and utilizes the 'fCWT' C++ library by Lukas Arts to make it
    available via an R package. See Arts, P.A. and Van den Broek, E.L. (2022)
    <doi:10.1038/s43588-021-00183-z> for details.
    The package includes some helpers, establishes a link to
    physical units and provides a plotting function.
